      "summary": "通过 ctypes 封装 HCCL（华为集合通信库）C 接口的 Python 绑定，提供 AllReduce、Broadcast、通信域初始化与销毁等分布式集合通信原语。",
      "tags": ["service", "hccl", "collective-communication", "ctypes-binding", "distributed"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 ctypes.CDLL 动态加载 HCCL 共享库，并将 torch dtype 与归约算子映射到 HCCL 枚举值。"
    },
    {
